         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">F. Von Mueller ¶ Thursday ¶ 1878 ¶  ¶ I feel honored, dear Mr Gibbs, ¶ Error for Gibbes, the long-term secretary,Victorian Academy of Arts. ¶  ¶ with your kind invitation on behalf of the council of t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">78.04.25</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Francis Gibbes</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">No. 580/(c), La Trobe Australian Manuscripts Collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">F. Von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Thursday</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">1878</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I feel honored, dear Mr Gibbs,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">Error for Gibbes, the long</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">-</seg>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">term secretary,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        </seg>Victorian Academy of Arts.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>with your kind invitation on behalf of the council of the Victorian Academy of arts, to witness the opening on Saturday,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The letter is dated on the basis of the report in the<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-style: italic; ">Argus</seg>,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>Monday 29 April 1878, p. 5: 'The eighth exhibition of the Victorian Academy of Arts was opened on Saturday afternoon by His Excellency the Governor. Sir George Bowen arrived shortly after 2 pm and was received by the president. There was no formal ceremonial of any kind…'.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>but I have to be from Friday til Monday on departmental engagements away from Melbourne<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>M to G. Berry,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>26 April 1878,<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>he announced that he was going to an unspecified place in the country until 29 April, but would continue to work there and maintain daily communication with his office.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>which arrangement prevents me to share in your festival.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Pray express to the Council my best gratitude for the consideration shown me.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
